Notes To Certificate : 					
					
1	Coherence of Form no 1 & 2 With Actual Expenditure is only concerned. As we are only Chartered Accountants and our knowledge and				
	 expertise is limited to verify only finacial figures of books of accounts. We are not technically Qualified & Competent to verify or				
	 certify Civil Engineer Or Architect Certificate as it being highly technical matter, Hence our Certification in above Form 3 is limited				
 	 to field of our Specialization only.				
					
2	Annexture to Form 3 has been Reprodused as submitted by Promotor and only finacial information with books of account has been				
	 verified by us. other information in annexture to form 3 like Name , PAN\Aadhar Number, and mobile number of allottes has been 				
	reproduced as submiited by promotor.				
					
3	So far as Encumberance Status is concerned, We are not technically & legally entitled to certify such charge. This falls exclusively under 				
	the jurisdiction of an advocate.				
					
4	We have filled only that data which were made available to us.				
					
5	Details of RERA Bank Account are given by Promotor and No details given for the Verification of the same.				
6. In Form 3 (Annexure) i.e.Statement for calculation of Receivables from the Real Estate Project Shop No.F003 to F012 are not for Sale but as part of Entire Project we had to mention that Shops in Annexure. Unit Amount for Shop No.F003 to F012 is Rs.0 each, but in Annexure to Form 3 uploaded Along with RERA Form 3 we have taken Unit Value for Shop No.F003 to F012 is Rs.1 for each as Utility for Annexure not accepted Rs.0 as Unit Amount.
